Multiple Payment Types:

Single payment (default)
Recurring payment subscriptions
Installment payment plans
Currency Selection:

Dropdown to select from multiple currencies
Visual feedback when currency changes
More Payment Methods:

Additional options for bank transfers
Credit card payments
Improved UI Elements:

Tab navigation for different payment types
Interactive forms with input highlighting
Loading states for payment processing
Animated transitions
